%% Data Flow Diagram - Text Generation Inference Server (TGIS)
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as KServe/ModelMesh<br/>gRPC Client
    participant Router as TGI Router<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant Tokenizer as Tokenizer<br/>(in-process)
    participant Batcher as Continuous Batcher<br/>(in-process)
    participant Shard as Model Shard(s)<br/>UDS gRPC
    participant GPU as GPU<br/>CUDA 12.1

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: Text Generation Request (gRPC)
    Client->>Router: GenerationService.Generate<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Tokenizer: Tokenize input text<br/>Function call
    Tokenizer-->>Router: Token IDs + attention mask
    Router->>Batcher: Add to batch queue<br/>Memory-aware scheduling
    Batcher->>Shard: Prefill batch<br/>UDS gRPC (no encryption)
    Shard->>GPU: CUDA inference<br/>Flash Attention v2
    GPU-->>Shard: Prefill result + first token
    loop Autoregressive Decoding
        Batcher->>Shard: NextToken request<br/>UDS gRPC
        Shard->>GPU: CUDA decode step
        GPU-->>Shard: Next token
        Shard-->>Batcher: Generated token
    end
    Batcher-->>Router: Complete generation result
    Router->>Tokenizer: Decode tokens to text
    Tokenizer-->>Router: Generated text
    Router-->>Client: GenerationResponse<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1b: Streaming Generation
    Client->>Router: GenerationService.GenerateStream<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP
    Router->>Shard: Prefill + decode loop<br/>UDS gRPC
    loop Token-by-Token Streaming
        Shard-->>Router: Single token
        Router-->>Client: StreamGenerationResponse<br/>gRPC server stream
    end

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: Health Check
    participant Kubelet as Kubelet
    Kubelet->>Router: GET /health<br/>HTTP 3000/TCP
    Router->>Shard: Health check<br/>UDS gRPC
    Shard->>GPU: Verify CUDA available
    GPU-->>Shard: CUDA OK
    Shard-->>Router: Healthy
    Router-->>Kubelet: 200 OK

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 3: Metrics Scrape
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    Prom->>Router: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP 3000/TCP
    Router-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(latency, tokens, batch sizes)
